## Finding: Implementation Dependency Graph and Complexity Assessment

### Gap Type: MISSING_SKILL
### Severity: CRITICAL
### Evidence: Loop 7 produced 6 solution specs. This loop defines their dependencies, complexity, and implementation sequencing.
### Proposed Resolution:

**DEPENDENCY GRAPH**

```
operational_readiness_gate (P0)
    ├── DEPENDS ON: All Phase 6 skills (validates outputs)
    ├── DEPENDS ON: Phase 7 existing skills (orchestrates their cadence)
    ├── REQUIRED BY: incident_response_operations (needs gate to establish on-call)
    ├── REQUIRED BY: slo_sla_management (needs gate to confirm SLOs are defined)
    └── PRODUCES: Phase 0 handoff document (loop-back artifact)

incident_response_operations (P0)
    ├── DEPENDS ON: operational_readiness_gate (establishes operational context)
    ├── DEPENDS ON: Phase 6 disaster_recovery (consumes runbooks)
    ├── DEPENDS ON: slo_sla_management (uses SLO targets for MTTR goals)
